TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Pull all Staged Claims for Distribution(s) in status of 15=Transmitting
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Staged_Claims

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DSTR.DSTR_GID, DSTR.POST_DT, TXN.INV_ID, TXN.MODEL_TYP_CD, TXN.VEND_ID, TXN.PICO_ID, TXN.CTRC_ID, TXN.AP_CO_CD, TXN.RPT_AP_CO_CD, TXN.PERIOD_ID, TXN.SNAP_APC_TYP_CD, TXN.AR_SER_4_ACCT_ID, TXN.AR_SER_5_ACCT_ID, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.ADMN_PEND_INV_AMT - coalesce(DROP.ADMN_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.ADMN_PEND_INV_AMT end ADMN_PEND_INV_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT + coalesce(DROP.ADMN_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT end ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT, TXN.ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11) then TXN.BASE_PEND_INV_AMT - coalesce(DROP.BASE_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.BASE_PEND_INV_AMT end BASE_PEND_INV_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT + coalesce(DROP.BASE_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT end BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT, TXN.BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11) then TXN.FRMLY_PEND_INV_AMT - coalesce(DROP.FRMLY_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.FRMLY_PEND_INV_AMT end FRMLY_PEND_INV_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT + coalesce(DROP.FRMLY_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT end FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT, TXN.FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.CTRC_PEND_INV_AMT - coalesce(DROP.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.CTRC_PEND_INV_AMT end CTRC_PEND_INV_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT + coalesce(DROP.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT end CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT, TXN.CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.PERF_PEND_INV_AMT - coalesce(DROP.PRFMC_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.PERF_PEND_INV_AMT end PERF_PEND_INV_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT + coalesce(DROP.PRFMC_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT end PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT, TXN.PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11 ) then TXN.PRC_PTCT_PEND_INV_AMT - coalesce(DROP.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.PRC_PTCT_PEND_INV_AMT end PRC_PTCT_PEND_INV_AMT, case when (DSTR.DSTR_CRTE_TYP_CD <> 11) then TXN.PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT + coalesce(DROP.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AT,0) else TXN.PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT end PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT, TXN.PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR DSTR inner join VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_TXN_STG TXN on (DSTR.DSTR_STAT_CD = 15 AND DSTR.DSTR_GID = TXN.DSTR_GID) left join VRAP.RCNT_DROP_CLM_INV_VAL DROP on (DSTR.DSTR_GID = DROP.DSTR_GID and DSTR.RECN_GID = DROP.RECN_GID and TXN.HVST_ID = DROP.HVST_ID and TXN.CLM_GID = DROP.CLM_GID)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LookUp into Rebate Payer for Vender Name and Abbreviated Name
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_Mfg_Payer

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: VEND_ID = VEND_ID_in AND MODEL_TYP_CD = MODEL_TYP_CD_in AND AR_SER_4_ACCT_ID = AR_SER_4_ACCT_ID_in AND AR_SER_5_ACCT_ID = AR_SER_5_ACCT_ID_in

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LookUp into Code Table for description of Business Entity
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_Bus_Entity

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT vrap.TVNDR_REBT_CD.CD_NM as CD_NM , vrap.TVNDR_REBT_CD.CD_NB as CD_NB FROM vrap.TVNDR_REBT_CD WHERE vrap.TVNDR_REBT_CD.TYP_CD=80

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Build all the data used for all the transaction types: RB, RF, PB, PF, BA, WO and RT
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_Build_Trans_Data

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF(SNAP_APC_TYP_CD = 5 , 'PB' , 'RB' )
--If PostAPC, then P. --If PreAPC or APC, the R ----This assumes that Outcomes will NOT have xB type transactions
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GL_DOC_TYP_CD_BOTH

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF(SNAP_APC_TYP_CD = 5 , 'PF' , 'RF' )
--If PostAPC, then P. --If PreAPC or APC, the R ----This assumes that Outcomes will NOT have xF type transactions
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GL_DOC_TYP_CD_FIXED

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
'??'
--We don't know what this needs to be set to, until the data is summarized. ----In the meantime, set the value to ??
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GL_DOC_TYP_CD_ADJ_FE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
'??'
--We don't know what this needs to be set to, until the data is summarized. ----In the meantime, set the value to ??
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GL_DOC_TYP_CD_ADJ_RB

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT + BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT + FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT + CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT + PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT + PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: PAY_AMT_AR5_var

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: DECODE(RTRIM(PERIOD_LEVEL) , 'QUARTER', SUBSTR(PERIOD_ID, 4, 2) || 'Q' || SUBSTR(PERIOD_ID, 3, 1) , 'MONTH', SUBSTR(PERIOD_PARENT_ID, 4, 2) || 'Q' || SUBSTR(PERIOD_PARENT_ID, 3, 1) || ' ' || SUBSTR(PERIOD_ID, 2, 2) , 'ERROR' )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: GL_PRD_ID
